# LinkedIn Organic Content Strategy for B2B SaaS — Research Repository

## What This Is

This repository contains primary research for building a playbook on **LinkedIn organic content strategy for B2B SaaS companies**. The goal is to collect high-signal, practitioner-sourced content from 10 experts who have actually used LinkedIn to generate pipeline — not just write about it.

The research will serve as the foundation for a practical, operator-ready playbook.

---

## Why I Chose This Topic

LinkedIn organic is the highest-ROI awareness channel available to early-stage and growth-stage B2B SaaS companies, with near-zero distribution cost and compounding returns. But most advice on the topic is either too generic ("post consistently!") or too tactical without strategic grounding.

The gap I want to close: **a practitioner-sourced playbook that connects LinkedIn content strategy to actual pipeline outcomes** — not vanity metrics. This requires learning from people who have built, measured, and iterated on LinkedIn as a revenue channel inside real B2B SaaS companies.

